h1 Intro
hr
p elkCSS is a result of the DRY principle, time and time again I've had to remake a base for websites, often taking valuable time to remind myself of documentation and properties. elk provides a simple base to build sites off in a sane and responsive fashion.
br
p elk is well suited for small websites, or those who don't want to hook in large frameworks. elk is a meant as a starting point, not a UI framework.
